Package se.liu.ida.hefquin.engine.federation.access.impl.cache

Class ChronicleMapCardinalityCache

java.lang.Object
se.liu.ida.hefquin.engine.federation.access.impl.cache.ChronicleMapCardinalityCache
Type Parameters:
K - The key type for caching cardinality responses.
All Implemented Interfaces:
Cache<CardinalityCacheKey,CardinalityCacheEntry>, PersistableCache<CardinalityCacheKey,CardinalityCacheEntry>
public class ChronicleMapCardinalityCache extends Object implements PersistableCache<CardinalityCacheKey,CardinalityCacheEntry>
A thread-safe persistent cache implementation for storing cardinality entries. This cache uses a ChronicleMap.
